@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry / User starts creating account
CreateAccount : do / Fill details
CreateAccount : exit / Account created

state "Watch Videos" as WatchVideos
WatchVideos : entry / User watches videos
WatchVideos : do / Watch videos
WatchVideos : exit / User stops watching

state "Upload Videos" as UploadVideos
UploadVideos : entry / User starts uploading
UploadVideos : do / Upload video
UploadVideos : exit / Video uploaded

state "Save Videos" as SaveVideos
SaveVideos : entry / User saves video
SaveVideos : do / Save video
SaveVideos : exit / Video saved

state "Enter Discussion" as EnterDiscussion
EnterDiscussion : entry / User enters discussion
EnterDiscussion : do / Participate in discussion
EnterDiscussion : exit / User exits discussion

state "Idle" <<choice>>

[*] --> CreateAccount

CreateAccount --> WatchVideos : [User creates account and watches videos]
CreateAccount --> UploadVideos : [User creates account and uploads videos]
CreateAccount --> SaveVideos : [User creates account and saves videos]
CreateAccount --> EnterDiscussion : [User creates account and enters discussion]

WatchVideos --> [*] : [User stops watching videos]

UploadVideos --> [*] : [User stops uploading videos]

SaveVideos --> [*] : [User stops saving videos]

EnterDiscussion --> [*] : [User exits discussion]

CreateAccount --> Idle <<choice>>
Idle : entry / User is idle
Idle : exit /
[*] --> Idle

@enduml
